      "date": "2013-03-14 19:12:51.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nJames, there is a separate question on whether this configurable parameter is needed at all anymore?  The maximum is now 1024 threads, though by default the number of threads automatically started is still capped at 256 or 512 (I _think_).\n\nIf you are not using this tunable at ORNL anymore, I'd prefer to just remove it, since it is inconsistent with the other thread tunables.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
